 Changelog (v1.0.0)
🚀 Initial release with PyQt6 GUI and full automation platform

🎯 Macro recording with anti-detection (bezier curves, randomized order, scroll drift)

🔒 Encrypted multi-account management with 6-digit verification

🌐 ProtonVPN integration and launch detection

🧠 Gameplay automation: auto-upgrade, collect, defend, attack patterns, events

💡 Visual macro editor with timeline and action properties

📋 Profile manager and secure credential handling

🧪 Scheduled tasks (⚠️ Beta feature)

🔄 Changelog and update fetch from GitHub

💾 Backup/Restore to external drives

🕵️‍♂️ Anti-debugging protection from Wireshark & debuggers

📊 Advanced logging system with export
